&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/minimum-time-to-complete-trips/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;2187. 完成旅途的最少时间 - 力扣（LeetCode）&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
